         </a>
                </div>

                <div class="category-item">
                  <a href="/products?category=ACCESSORIES" style="text-decoration: none; color: inherit; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;">

                    <div class="category-img-wrapper">
